Class PhylogeneticTree

java.lang.Object
org.jscience.biology.phylogeny.PhylogeneticTree
public class PhylogeneticTree extends Object
Phylogenetic tree construction and representation.

Supports multiple tree construction algorithms:

  • UPGMA (Unweighted Pair Group Method with Arithmetic Mean)
  • Neighbor-Joining

Integrates with the JScience Tree interface for graph-theoretic operations.

* @author Silvere Martin-Michiellot
